Question: The right image shows an adult gorilla on all fours in front of multiple other gorillas.

Reference Answer: False

Right image URL: https://images.huffingtonpost.com/2012-08-18-westernlowlandsilverback.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there an adult gorilla on all fours in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many other gorillas are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1} > 1')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
